@kong_base_url = http://localhost:18000
@audit_log_base_url = http://localhost:8082
@event_id = REPLACE_WITH_EVENT_ID

### Audit health - direct service
GET {{audit_log_base_url}}/actuator/health

### List current tenant activity - tenant1 through Kong
GET {{kong_base_url}}/api/audit-events?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{tenant1_token}}
X-Request-Id: audit-tenant1-list-001

### List current tenant activity - tenant2 through Kong
GET {{kong_base_url}}/api/audit-events?limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{tenant2_token}}
X-Request-Id: audit-tenant2-list-001

### Get one event by eventId - tenant1 through Kong
GET {{kong_base_url}}/api/audit-events/{{event_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{tenant1_token}}
X-Request-Id: audit-tenant1-one-001

### Missing token - expected 401
GET {{kong_base_url}}/api/audit-events
X-Request-Id: audit-missing-token-001
